text: Tjoeij Lin Alienilin is an Indonesian archer. She was born on 25 August 1943. Lin Alienilin competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics.Tjoeij Lin AlienilinTjoeij Lin ALIENILIN == References == Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian archers Category:Olympians for Indonesia
